text: I’m also going to start a “privacy vs confidentiality” discussion, now that we have a mail distro list… will do by EOW… <@U0KM97TRP> do you want to include a distro list for the Arch-WG, if so let me know what the name is…. we want to make sure we have a clear definition as people seem to use the terms interchangeable.

<@U0W7D64LC> Agree that confidentiality and privacy are not identical/interchangeable. Would be good to get our terminology/vocabulary clarified. The Arch-wg mail-list is: <mailto:hyperledger-arch-wg@lists.hyperledger.org|hyperledger-arch-wg@lists.hyperledger.org>
